<TITLE> Eve-teasers beware! </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Mar 12 (bdnews24.com)  The police is making a list of eve-teasers. They will then, notify parents of their errant wards. Dhaka Metropolitan Police Commissioner Shahidul Haq said on Friday that a list of eve-teasers in Dhaka is being drawn up. He said this at a programme on the activities of Community Police at Mirpur Shah Ali Police Station at noon. Haq said, "A list of eve-teasers is being drawn up at every police station. It will be sent to their guardians so that they might better guide their children." The community police is having to deal with a hing number of complaints of eve-teasing in the Mirpur area, the official said. He also said that local crime rates had decreased with the introduction of Community Police and urged the people for their assistance. b
